%% Activity Diagram
sequenceDiagram
title GameFace User Interaction Flow
actor User
participant "Web Client" as WebClient
participant "Signaling Server" as SignalingServer
participant "Media Server" as MediaServer
participant "Database" as Database  

User -> WebClient: Open GameFace App
WebClient -> SignalingServer: Request Auth Token
SignalingServer -> Database: Verify User Credentials
Database -->> SignalingServer: Return User Data
SignalingServer -->> WebClient: Return Auth Token
WebClient -> SignalingServer: Start Game Session
SignalingServer -> Database: Create Game Session
Database -->> SignalingServer: Return Session ID
SignalingServer -->> WebClient: Return Game Session Info
WebClient -->> User: Display Game Session Info
User -> WebClient: Join Game Session
WebClient -> SignalingServer: Request to Join Session
SignalingServer -> Database: Update Session Participants
Database -->> SignalingServer: Confirm Participant Added
SignalingServer -->> WebClient: Confirm Join Success
WebClient -->> User: Display Joined Session Info
User -> WebClient: Send In-Game Action
WebClient -> SignalingServer: Process In-Game Action
SignalingServer -> Database: Update Game State
Database -->> SignalingServer: Confirm Game State Updated
SignalingServer -->> WebClient: Return Updated Game State
WebClient -->> User: Display Updated Game State
User -> WebClient: Leave Game Session
WebClient -> SignalingServer: Request to Leave Session
SignalingServer -> Database: Update Session Participants
Database -->> SignalingServer: Confirm Participant Removed
SignalingServer -->> WebClient: Confirm Leave Success
WebClient -->> User: Display Session Left Confirmation
User -> WebClient: Logout
WebClient -> SignalingServer: Invalidate Auth Token
SignalingServer -> Database: Update User Status
Database -->> SignalingServer: Confirm Status Updated
SignalingServer -->> WebClient: Confirm Logout Success
WebClient -->> User: Display Logout Confirmation
%% End of Activity Diagram %% 